# Form Input like Material Design Specification using only CSS3

## What happens? Behaviour

out of focus    Label is bigger + Bottom border color is grey
in focus        Label shrinks + Bottom border color is blue
on Error        Bottom border is red and HINT is suggested

## CSS Properties to use

- display
- position
- width
- height
- z-index

## Advanced CSS

- input:focus
- input:valid
- input:focus + label , label style is affected each time input is clicked
- transition property: all 0.3s ease on label
